### List roles
GET http://localhost:3000/roleMaster?page=1&pageSize=20&search=admin&status=ACTIVE

### Add a role
POST http://localhost:3000/roleMaster/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleCode": "ADMIN",
  "roleName": "Administrator",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "permissions": {
    "basicMaster": { "scopes": ["VIEW", "EDIT"] },
    "customerManagement": { "scopes": ["VIEW", "CREATE", "EDIT"] }
  }
}

### Get role by id
GET http://localhost:3000/roleMaster/ROL-001

### Edit role
PUT http://localhost:3000/roleMaster/edit/ROL-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName": "Admin",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "ifMatchVersion": 1
}

### Get all permissions for a role
GET http://localhost:3000/roleMaster/ROL-001/permissions

### Get permission for module customerManagement
GET http://localhost:3000/roleMaster/ROL-001/permissions/customerManagement

### Upsert permission for module customerManagement
PUT http://localhost:3000/roleMaster/ROL-001/permissions/customerManagement
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scopes": ["VIEW", "CREATE", "EDIT", "EXPORT"],
  "ifMatchVersion": 1
}

